{"tid":806730,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賤朗空虛 (賤朗空虛) 無人交波似廢堆 賤朗空虛 (賤朗空虛) 王騎這晚你屬誰","createTime":"2018-09-05T02:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T02:29:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4d555ba54b5afba7a74a3a42aca8c1e93d52a4fa","tid":806730,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"賤朗空虛<br />\n<br />\n作詞：王騎    作曲：水谷公生<br />\n<br />\n賤朗一個角落裡 獨食似黑暗作伴侶<br />\n隔數張木台那處 是對年青愛侶<br />\n<br />\n皇馬此際正在播 浪射朗喜歡哼的歌<br />\n碎了的心再碎 獨跌坐失意裡<br />\n閉起眼睛想過去<br />\n<br />\n賤朗空虛 (賤朗空虛)<br />\n無人交波似廢堆<br />\n賤朗空虛 (賤朗空虛)<br />\n王騎這晚你屬誰"},{"pid":"fcd154e6fc1a0b55f3d771adbf40d33e7afab5dd","tid":806730,"uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"意甲頓變了乏味!<br />\n但願朗沒往昔　但願朗沒記憶<br />\n永不想你 (永不想你)"},{"pid":"4a75a226c56ab11c82eedd3db6bbb1d7e778ffc4","tid":806730,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed50cf20ddae01c8cb5116ec34e0e1fec780fa3","tid":806730,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:53:32.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ab6a2b29560ff608aa11f94c2b85658a525deb","tid":806730,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2946b503d631a1e0501e12669846bd8fa03676e2","tid":806730,"uid":52122,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"我想問好耐師兄其實你心底係未好撚愛牙朗？<br />\n同奧瑪同一樣人黎？"},{"pid":"fee10843fc89557646fa3089c923d5c497ed07fb","tid":80